BUGFIX: Incomplete implementation of the WindowNext and WindowPrev Macro arguments finished. (reported by Christoph Gutjahr)

 @{MC "V3.24"}

CHANGED: IRCom support wasn't up to date and caused crashes.@{par}
FEATURE: There is now an about requester.@{par}
CHANGED: Many changes to this manual. (Danke Hans-Jörg 'Otti' Ottinger)@{par}
BUGFIX: Hopefully fixed OS4 final problems. (Thanks to Michael Merkel)

 @{MC "V3.25"}

BUGFIX: Fixed a nasty bug that caused to loose qualifiers under some
circumstances. This version should no longer cause problem with EUAE, Mame,
RDesktop and any other program it effected.

 @{MC "V3.26"}

BUGFIX: Missing multimedia data file with alias information caused hotkey
entering to fail without any reason.

 @{MC "V3.27"}
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       

CHANGED: It's now possible to ignore outdated or missing mcc classes. This of
course won't work if the classes are missing, but it allows to use the
application without updating and restarting the system.

 @{MC "V4.0"}

CHANGED: Massive code changes and optimizations.@{par}

 @{MC "V4.10"}

CHANGED: Massive code changes and optimizations.@{par}
