@node "Buglist" "Buglist"

@{MS "Buglist"}

@{b}Amiga version@{ub}

When pressing many keys at the same time the whole keyboard handling is
freezing! The problem is the keyboard protocol. The amiga keyboard is just
sending one up and down message for each key, but the PC keyboard is auto
repeating key down messages.@{par}

@{b}Amithlon version@{ub}@{par}

/

